data.title: The 100 Best Movies With Princess in the Title
data.meta_description: Over 60 filmgoers have voted on the 100 Best Movies With Princess in the Title. Current Top 3: A Little Princess, The Princess Bride, The Swan Princess
data.text:
Ranked By

479 votes

68 voters

How many movies with princess in the title can you name? This list ranks the best movies with princess in the name, whether they're documentaries, dramas, horror movies, or any other genre of film. Do you have a favorite movie with princess in the title? Categorizing movies by words in their titles is kind of uncommon, but that's a big part of why this list is so fun to scroll through. There's probably one movie with princess in the title you think of right away, but you might be shocked to see how many others exist as well.

Notable films with princess in the title include The Princess Bride, The Princess and the Frog, and Princess Mononoke, although there are many more examples on this list. This poll is interactive, meaning you can vote the princess movies up or down depending on how much you like them.

Eleanor Bron, Liam Cunningham, Liesel Matthews

A heartwarming adaptation of Frances Hodgson Burnett's classic novel, this film showcases a young girl's journey of perseverance and faith amidst adversity. Its beautiful cinematography and captivating performances make for an enchanting movie experience, perfect for family movie nights.

Released : 1995

Directed by : Alfonso Cuarón

Filled with romance, adventure, and tongue-in-cheek humor, this beloved cult classic has enchanted audiences for decades. With unforgettable characters and unforgettable dialogue, it's no wonder it remains a fan favorite and one of the most quotable films of all time.
